# Backend (apps/api): Fastify standards

- Keep routes thin: route -> service -> repository (or direct data access) -> schema validation.
- Validate all input at the boundary using the shared domain schemas (do not trust frontend payloads).
- Expose explicit, predictable read-only APIs for dashboard data; avoid magic behavior and implicit side effects.
- Financial logic belongs in the rules engine layer; backend should orchestrate/persist, not calculate.
- Prefer deterministic/predictable error handling:
  - return clear error messages
  - log actionable details
- For any change, include a verification plan (unit tests + integration surface if applicable).
